question.en:
Consider the following code:

@Injectable({ scope: Scope.TRANSIENT })
class UserService {}

@Injectable()
class OrderService {
  constructor(private userService: UserService) {}
}

What happens when two requests arrive and each OrderService instance needs UserService?

